<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Std on miyan的博客</title><link>https://miyan.site/tags/std/</link><description>Recent content in Std on miyan的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 10 May 2025 18:26:21 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://miyan.site/tags/std/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>使用std::make_unique_for_overwrite创建一个char数组当缓冲区</title><link>https://miyan.site/p/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8stdmake_unique_for_overwrite%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AAchar%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E5%BD%93%E7%BC%93%E5%86%B2%E5%8C%BA/</link><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://miyan.site/p/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8stdmake_unique_for_overwrite%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AAchar%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E5%BD%93%E7%BC%93%E5%86%B2%E5%8C%BA/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="起因">起因
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>看到这个&lt;a class="link" href="https://microcai.org/2024/11/16/do-not-new-a-buffer.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>博客&lt;/a>里写道这样写进行了初始化操作&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-c++" data-lang="c++">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">auto&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">buffer_size&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">*&lt;/span>&lt;span class="mi">1024&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">*&lt;/span>&lt;span class="mi">1024&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">auto&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">buffer&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">std&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">::&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">make_unique&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kt">char&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">[]&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">buffer_size&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">);&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>评论区jajuju提出可以使用创建buffer&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>其实这里的情况是 make_unique 里用的 new 表达式是 &lt;code>new T[n]()&lt;/code> ，对于 char 数组会进行零初始化。
如果换用 make_unique_for_overwrite，里面的 new 表达式就是 &lt;code>new T[n]&lt;/code>，此时进行默认初始化，就不会给 char 数组内容清零。&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>瞬间感觉学到了一个新知识，这个&lt;code>make_unique_for_overwrite&lt;/code>真是第一次见了(没看过cppreference上的make_unique一节&amp;hellip;)&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="源码分析">源码分析
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>我们以&lt;a class="link" href="https://en.cppreference.com/w/cpp/memory/unique_ptr/make_unique" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>cppreference&lt;/a>上的实现分析下源码：&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>非数组类型&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-c++" data-lang="c++">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">template&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">class&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nc">T&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">requires&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">!&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">std&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">::&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">is_array_v&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">T&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">std&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">::&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">unique_ptr&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">T&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;gt;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">make_unique_for_overwrite&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">return&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">std&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">::&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">unique_ptr&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">T&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">new&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">T&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">);&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>效果类似于 new T，但没有 ()，因此不会执行默认初始化（特别是对于 POD 类型）。&lt;/li>
&lt;li>构造函数仍然会被调用（如果 T 不是 POD）。&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;ol start="2">
&lt;li>
&lt;p>动态数组&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-c++" data-lang="c++">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">template&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">class&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nc">T&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">requires&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">std&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">::&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">is_unbounded_array_v&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">T&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">std&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">::&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">unique_ptr&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">T&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;gt;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">make_unique_for_overwrite&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">std&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">::&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">size_t&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">n&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">return&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">std&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">::&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">unique_ptr&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">T&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">new&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">std&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">::&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">remove_extent_t&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">T&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">n&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">]);&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>分配 n 个 T 元素的未初始化数组，不调用 ()，因此不会默认初始化（类似 new T[n]）。&lt;/li>
&lt;li>不会调用构造函数（如果 T 是 POD）。&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;ol start="3">
&lt;li>
&lt;p>禁止定长数组&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-c++" data-lang="c++">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">template&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">class&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nc">T&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">class&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">... &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nc">Args&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">requires&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">std&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">::&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">is_bounded_array_v&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">T&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kt">void&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">make_unique_for_overwrite&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">Args&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">...)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">delete&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>因为定长数组不能通过 new 进行动态分配，所以编译时禁止。&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="参考">参考
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/microsoft/STL/blob/main/stl/inc/memory#L3618" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>MSVC STL实现&lt;/a>&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>